    We use SF UI Display for headings and SF UI Text for body fonts.
  %p
    %strong For the fonts to work properly in your app, copy /spec/test_app/public/fonts to the public directory of your app.

= card 'Headings, Paragraphs, and Common Styles' do

  = haml_example do
    :plain

      %h1 This is an H1
      %h2 This is an H3
      %h3 This is an H3
      %h3 This is an H3
      %h4 This is an H4
      %h5 This is an H5
      %p.featured-large This is Large Featured Text
      %p.featured This is Featured Text
      %p.note This is Note Text - often used for module descriptions under titles
      %p This is a paragraph -- use this for body text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Cras feugiat tincidunt laoreet. Ut venenatis in libero at posuere. Vestibulum ac rhoncus purus. Etiam elementum diam sit amet arcu commodo elementum.

%hr
